Package: longHM
Title: High-dimensional mediation analysis in longitudinal studies
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yidan Cui [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yidan Cui <amber_cui@sjtu.edu.cn>
Description: This is an effective and novel approach for high-dimensional 
    mediation analysis in longitudinal data, incorporating variable selection 
    and indirect effect assessment using both the linear mixed-effects model 
    and the generalized estimating equation.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
